          Want to manage the emails you receive from us? You can update your preferences here, unsubscribe here, or view our privacy policy here.
        </p> -->
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;">Address: Magdalo Streets, La Paz, Iloilo City, Philippines</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>

</html>
